727,872712,Rush: Cinema Strangiato - R40+ Director's Cut,"Following the success of Rush: Cinema Strangiato - Director's Cut in movie theaters worldwide, Anthem Entertainment and Trafalgar Releasing give Rush fans around the world the opportunity to experience it again – this time from the comfort of home.  In celebration 40 years of Moving Pictures, this global streaming release features the “director’s cut” of 2019's R40+ event that was just shown in cinemas, giving audiences a special look into R40 LIVE, with a setlist including this year’s new additions of bonus tracks ""One Little Victory"" and “Red Barchetta” as well as ""Cygnus X-1 / “The Story So Far” featuring Neil's final recorded drum solo masterpiece.",2021-09-09,10.6736,7.0,1
728,289899,Beim nächsten Mann wird alles anders,,1989-01-12,10.6665,3.4,5
