782,1462591,Hot Line,"Malena, a woman who divides her life between two jobs: by night she's a dancer in a cabaret and by day she answers a ""Hot Line,"" an erotic telephone line. However, her routine turns into a nightmare when a serial killer begins calling her, recounting his crimes in chilling detail and announcing that she will be his next victim. This is a clear homage to the Italian Giallo.HoH",2025-10-28,10.2761,7.5,2
