1324,1717023,Half Emirati,Half Emirati is a documentary that explores the social implications of being the offspring of a mixed marriage between a native of the United Arab Emirates and any other nationality.  Five of these Emirati nationals share their experiences and stories about what it is really like to be only 'half' among those who are 'pure'.,2012-12-12,6.971,0.0,0
