2534,694,The Shining,"Jack Torrance accepts a caretaker job at the Overlook Hotel, where he, along with his wife Wendy and their son Danny, must live isolated from the rest of the world for the winter. But they aren't prepared for the madness that lurks within.",1980-05-23,13.9826,8.203,19078
2535,1173357,The Devil in Her,A husband buys his wife a ring only to find out it belonged to a crazy woman who had committed suicide and is now terrorizing the family as a ghost.,1974-11-27,13.9761,7.0,1
