2853,1516108,Kino Kino,"Three friends - Mahir (the actor), Bahram (the director) and Firuz (the screenwriter) want to make a film on a serious topic. However, no investor helps them. The friends, left in despair, decide to make the film on their own account. Mahir wants to sell his car, Bahram the gold he took from the house, and Firuz wants to make the film by selling the ancient carpet in their house.",2019-05-18,10.3486,0.0,0
