3599,1468688,An Island Away From You,"A romantic comedy set in the breathtaking Canary Islands. After being left at the altar, uptight chef Harry is convinced by his best friend to escape to her homeland, Gran Canaria. There, amid stunning beaches, vibrant culture, and delicious cuisine, Harry rediscovers joy—and unexpectedly falls in love with his best friend's father. Woven with humor, heart, and sun-soaked adventures, the film is a celebration of second chances and the power of unexpected love.",2026-04-10,7.07,6.2,4
