6233,1729527,Rampas Cintaku,"The story of Riz, a young bachelor desperate to escape the clutches of debt, poverty and loan shark harassment. He makes the decision to work at a nightclub for higher wages. There, he meets a wealthy and renowned businesswoman named Datin Safieya. Despite being married to Dato Jeffri, Datin Safieya seduces Rizal and promises him a luxurious life if he agrees to be her boyfriend. With its intricate plot, My Stolen Love is sure to keep viewers on the edge of their seats and wondering what will happen next.",2022-01-01,4.2411,0.0,0
