6931,699139,Young Girl,"Na-kyeong and Hoon are secretly having a fling. They had a fluttering first kiss and it only made them worry. Na-kyeong calls her best friend Jeong-hee to ask for advice on how far she should go about her relationship with her fling. On their next date, Na-kyeong follows Jeong-hee’s advice and will have her first sex…",2020-04-09,3.9599,0.0,0
