8117,418956,The Ugly Duckling,An outcast duckling's search for a family to accept him leads to constant rejection before learning his true identity as a swan.,1939-04-07,3.6119,6.992,189
8118,12118,Police Academy 3: Back in Training,"When police funding is cut, the Governor announces he must close one of the academies. To make it fair, the two police academies must compete against each other to stay in operation. Mauser persuades two officers in Lassard's academy to better his odds, but things don't quite turn out as expected...",1986-03-20,3.6119,5.816,1385
