8560,18861,Naruto the Movie: Guardians of the Crescent Moon Kingdom,"Naruto Uzumaki, Kakashi Hatake, Sakura Haruno, and Rock Lee are assigned to protect the prince of the Land of the Moon, Michiru, during his world trip; other escorts had been hired, but quit due to being treated poorly. The Land of the Moon is a very wealthy nation, so Michiru tends to buy whatever he wants, and has a very materialistic worldview. His Hikaru, also acts in much the same manner.",2006-08-05,3.5084,7.099,489
8561,1728531,The Crossroads of Destiny,"The film is a romantic drama that portrays the love story of young people, focusing on the mysterious ways of fate that bring together two lovers (or young individuals) with different backgrounds and personalities.  Kyaw Hein’s Acting Debut  This film was the first movie that U Kyaw Hein acted in before becoming a leading actor, marking a historic beginning in his artistic career.  A Memorable Theme Song  The film’s theme song, “Phu Sar Lan Sone” (The Crossroads of Destiny), became widely popular across generations and remains deeply cherished in the hearts of audiences to this day.",,3.5081,0.0,0
