9362,1607159,A Room Called Home,"Set in an old apartment complex where a family lives in a single cramped room, Nhà Ba Tôi Một Phòng portrays the “out-of-sync” relationship between a conservative father and his dream-filled Gen Z daughter. As generational differences collide within the confined space, their bond is tested and gradually mended. The film offers an intimate slice of contemporary Vietnamese family life, where love often begins with understanding.",2026-02-17,3.3462,0.0,0
