9724,1707281,Nena,"Set in the summer of 1980 (or 1987 in some regions) in Spain, this film explores the themes of freedom and awakening. A woman named Estela takes her young children, Marc and Empar, to spend a few days with her sister Lola and her husband Eduardo. It is the children’s first time away from their separating parents. Through the eyes of the 10-year-old son, Marc, the family discovers the hidden romance between his aunt Lola and Elsa, an attractive actress spending the summer nearby. The narrative follows Lola as she dares to explore a homosexual love story for the very first time.",2025-10-27,3.2815,7.0,1
