10547,382517,Open Season: Scared Silly,"The humans and animals believe a werewolf is on the loose, and former hunter Shaw uses the opportunity to re-open the season. Boog, Elliot, and Mr. Weenie have to face their fears and find the werewolf to get the season closed permanently.",2015-12-18,3.1493,6.0,392
