10559,1492288,La chaleur,"It’s unusually hot on the beaches of the Landes, and 17-year-old Marouane is spending his last day at the campground with a nagging fear: will the body he buried on the beach the day before be discovered? Marouane also wonders if he might be falling in love with the charming Giulia.",2026-07-08,3.1473,6.615,13
10560,1707281,Nena,"Set in the summer of 1980 (or 1987 in some regions) in Spain, this film explores the themes of freedom and awakening. A woman named Estela takes her young children, Marc and Empar, to spend a few days with her sister Lola and her husband Eduardo. It is the children’s first time away from their separating parents. Through the eyes of the 10-year-old son, Marc, the family discovers the hidden romance between his aunt Lola and Elsa, an attractive actress spending the summer nearby. The narrative follows Lola as she dares to explore a homosexual love story for the very first time.",2025-10-27,3.2815,7.0,1
